WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.769 --> 00:00:01.710
When the work is complete,

1
00:00:01.769 --> 00:00:03.170
the task can be closed.

2
00:00:04.280 --> 00:00:07.380
Locate the Closure Information section at the bottom of the task form.

3
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.149
In the Close Notes field,

4
00:00:09.560 --> 00:00:11.800
provide clear information describing what was completed.

5
00:00:13.859 --> 00:00:16.068
Then click Close Task to save your changes.

6
00:00:16.940 --> 00:00:19.260
Provided all required fields have been completed,

7
00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:22.280
the task State moves to Closed Complete.

8
00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:25.959
If additional tasks or approvals are required as part of the fulfillment process,

9
00:00:26.540 --> 00:00:28.959
they can be viewed on the related Requested Item record.

10
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:32.200
In this example,

11
00:00:32.409 --> 00:00:34.459
no additional tasks or approvals are required,

12
00:00:34.540 --> 00:00:36.099
so the request is also completed.
